short.ar: اختر من بين 3 أوضاع مختلفة في لعبة الحوض هذه وابدأ اللعبة.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Do you like to feed fish! Heal the fishes, clean the aquariums and start the fun.

How To Play
Played with Mouse.

Aquarium Arcade Game Features
✓ Little sounds
✓ 4+ Fish
✓ Basic control
✓ 2D Environment

Finally, you can enjoy these game for free (and more requests will be added)! Aquarium Arcade Game extension does not contain any hidden ads.
